{"tid":1136111,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"埋綫雙眼皮建議","createTime":"2019-05-02T19:21:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-01T02:14:52.000Z","uid":163765,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"3e93ffcaffb5a5b766c52cac242b0885b8e75905","tid":1136111,"uid":163765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T19:21:46.000Z","msg":"天生眼皮脂肪多 一向有痴雙眼皮膠水嘅習慣 痴左大半年<br />\n最近有隻眼膠水敏感 紅左同甩皮 痴唔到雙眼皮 <br />\n上網睇過埋綫雙眼皮 整出嚟嘅效果比較自然 好想試下 <br />\n但咨詢過幾間細舖 都話要抽脂 <br />\n真係好想整雙眼皮 化妝易啲 睇嚟又精神啲 依家單眼皮個樣長期睇落未瞓醒😭<br />\n<br />\n想問下各位大佬 有冇整埋線雙眼皮地方嘅建議？"},{"pid":"efe968f3118b919f1c1ec237bc6d7f6220558f9c","tid":1136111,"uid":231601,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T19:25:12.000Z","msg":"我都想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雙眼皮 不過又係眼皮勁多脂肪 腫到兩邊俾蚊咬咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又成日俾人話眼腫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2e11729c5aaa5e43e8ea09482603bc477c7e692","tid":1136111,"uid":163765,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"efe968f3118b919f1c1ec237bc6d7f6220558f9c","tid":1136111,"uid":231601,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T19:25:12.000Z","msg":"我都想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雙眼皮 不過又係眼皮勁多脂肪 腫到兩邊俾蚊咬咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又成日俾人話眼腫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T19:26:52.000Z","msg":"咁誇張 比蚊咬好似真係好嚴重<br />\n問左幾間 眼皮多脂肪都要抽脂 好糾結 <br />\n好似風險好大 失敗左真係柒出國際"},{"pid":"dbf8363390810908cadb022a83fd5621f30fc015","tid":1136111,"uid":210739,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T14:13:29.000Z","msg":"台灣個d好似可以又抽脂有埋線<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df880